# --- Claude & Anthropic 完整规则集 (2026.04 深度优化版) ---
# 优先级建议：置于分流规则顶部
# 兼容 OpenClash DOMAIN/DOMAIN-SUFFIX/DOMAIN-KEYWORD/GEOSITE 语法

# --- 核心域名 (Core Domains) ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,anthropic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claude.ai
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claude.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,clau.de
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,anthropic.cloud
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,anthropic.io
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,anthropic.dev
DOMAIN,api.anthropic.com
DOMAIN,api-eu.anthropic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,typeform.com

# --- 客户端与内容分发 (MCP & Artifacts & CDN) ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claudemcpclient.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claudeusercontent.com
DOMAIN,cdn.anthropic.com
DOMAIN,anthropic.com.cdn.cloudflare.net
DOMAIN,servd-anthropic-website.b-cdn.net
DOMAIN,anthropic-static.s3.amazonaws.com

# --- 认证与内容管理 (Auth & CMS) ---
DOMAIN,anthropic.auth0.com
DOMAIN,anthropic-com.ghost.io

# --- 监控、遥测与功能开关 (Telemetry & Feature Gates) ---
# 必须走代理，否则会导致功能受限或 IP 环境异常检测
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,statsig.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,statsigapi.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,featuregates.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,launchdarkly.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,sentry.io
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,datadog
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,sentry
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,sift

# --- NTP 时区检测 (关键：防止时区泄露) ---
# 确保 NTP 请求走代理以匹配节点出口时区
GEOSITE,category-ntp

# --- 兜底关键词与通配规则 ---
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,anthropic
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,claude
GEOSITE,anthropic